@startuml 01_system_context
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam rectangleBorderColor #555555
skinparam rectangleFontSize 13
skinparam databaseBorderColor #555555
skinparam noteBorderColor #AAAAAA
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFFFF0
skinparam arrowColor #333333

title System Context - Score Update & Live Leaderboard

rectangle "User\n(Browser / App)" as User #DDEEFF
rectangle "External Auth Service\n(Out of scope)" as AuthService #FFF9C4
rectangle "API Server\n(This Module)" as APIServer #C8E6C9
database "PostgreSQL\n(Persistent Store)" as DB #B3E5FC
database "Redis\n(Cache & Pub/Sub)" as Redis #FFCCBC
rectangle "Other Connected\nClients" as Clients #DDEEFF

User --> APIServer : POST /api/v1/scores/update
User --> APIServer : WS /ws/scoreboard
AuthService ..> APIServer : issues JWT verified here
APIServer --> DB : persist score & processed_actions
APIServer --> Redis : ZADD leaderboard / PUBLISH event
APIServer --> Clients : scoreboard:update via WebSocket

note right of APIServer
  This module owns:
  - Score update REST endpoint
  - WebSocket hub
  - Rate limiting
  - Idempotency guard
  - Leaderboard cache management
end note

note right of AuthService
  Tokens are issued externally.
  This module only verifies them.
end note

@enduml
